Stochastic Resonance -
http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.31.4076



The objective for both is to extract and amplify &quot;boundary&quot; information from
the distribution, as opposed to &quot;target&quot; information.



